      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SECRET BANDIT (1) ran below her best last time finishing fourth (29.71) over 520m at Richmond in a NG. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from six starts. Looks the one to beat on her best form. HOW HIGH (2) is a handy type who notched his 4th career success when too good (25.54) from Box 2 at this track. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Has definite claims. WHERE'S FERNANDO (7) is an honest type who is having his first look at course. Was an effortless winner last time scoring by 5.5 lengths at Nowra (20.15). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Bold showing expected again. CUMBRIA BENNY (8) was in the money last time at Bulli (22.70) in a NG, finishing a 1.75 lengths second. Has already won four times from this draw.",
